comments.content: Or Letraset's DIN 16/17. Not square enough to be [Isonorm](http://web.archive.org/web/20131015205037/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/urw/isonorm/).

Interesting. Looks like a mix between [Praxis](http://web.archive.org/web/20131015205037/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/ef/praxis/ef-regular/testdrive.html?s=n%20a%20%EF%20v%20e&p=96) and   
Mecanorma's Normalis
